Package io.github.scru128

Class Scru128Id

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.scru128.Scru128Id
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Scru128Id>
    public final class Scru128Id
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Scru128Id>, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a SCRU128 ID and provides converters to/from String and 128-bit unsigned integer.

    This class is designed to be an immutable data class, and thus the reference to an object can be safely copied and shared by multiple variables without calling the clone() method.
